## Prerequisites

This project uses [mise](https://mise.jdx.dev/) for managing tool versions. Install mise and then run:

```bash
mise install
```

This will install the required versions of Java and SBT.

## Building and Running

### Compile the project
```bash
sbt compile
```

### Run the application
```bash
sbt run
```

### Run tests
```bash
sbt test
```

### Create a package
```bash
sbt package
```

